'''Note:''' Scratch operator blocks (<code>+</code>, <code>-</code>, <code>*</code>, <code>/</code>, <code>mod</code>, comparisons, <code>and</code>, <code>or</code>, math operations) are all supported inside shader hats and are compiled to their WGSL equivalents. Fragment-shader-only functions (<code>dpdx</code>, <code>textureSample</code>, etc.) are intentionally excluded.

